{"tid":1474580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟係咪想冇人出黎呀？","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:39:06.000Z","uid":23046,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ce79cd8a16d61bdf7fb0f25a899017520ecd0b86","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"屌！檢討差唔多夠喇，係時候做文宣集氣喇<br />\n<br />\n政府辣著唔同火頭<br />\n雖然大家都好興<br />\n但望一望出面？<br />\n<br />\n一個大post講下一步出去邊都冇呀<br />\n有人過圍稅局<br />\n又冇圍<br />\n又話再搞不合作，又冇左<br />\n817係咪幾個地方集會？<br />\n818又話行？<br />\n但想問下有幾多人知detail？<br />\n又有幾多人知時間表？<br />\n又有幾多人知果日出去做咩？<br />\n<br />\n係～我知實有人想講<br />\n係你自己唔留意姐？<br />\n<br />\n但係 係咪個個都24小時mon每一個 post？<br />\n係咪淨係需要跟得最貼既人出？<br />\n記住我地目標唔止係同溫層呀！<br />\n<br />\n而家資訊已經越來越多，越來越亂<br />\n所以更要努力集中谷人氣，如果唔係咩都搞唔成<br />\n<br />\n仲有得罪講句，唔係分化<br />\n就算連登mon得貼既都唔多人啦<br />\n仲要入面都會有人係冷氣軍師<br />\n<br />\n最近幾次好多都係出事先再有人出去支援<br />\n仲要都係話我地<span style=\"color: red;\">冇咩人</span>佢就放彈清場<br />\n<br />\n係咪團火熄喇？<br />\n未就幫手宣傳！<br />\n<br />\n連我隔離位個港豬同事都笑話係咪謝喇！<br />\n爭氣啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再打飛機話咩就贏啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係<br />\n希望文宣實用性可以再高番啲<br />\n做到宣傳作用<br />\n而家果啲係好靚<br />\n但真係少左人留意，帶比人既資訊亦少左<br />\n果啲叫人出去遊行集會既文宣可以比多啲資訊架<br />\n資訊性既野可以再清楚啲<br />\n又或者加多d圖吸引人出去<br />\n又或者講解下發生咩事架<br />\n<br />\n而家果啲真係有少少華而不實<br />\n我地唔可以淨係顧住靚，顧住年輕人target<br />\n而唔記得左其他人架！<br />\n講多次！<br />\n目標唔止係同溫層呀！<br />\n<br />\n加油！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xnyrtue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxnyrtue.jpg&h=baad92b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/440mhxn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F440mhxn.jpg&h=e3478235&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXfdS5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXfdS5H.jpg&h=b6c2f35e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9L9rqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9L9rqJ.jpg&h=c1ec00ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f242cb9ed4cdf11628e7e651a67d3e729ffa2288","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"再開再推，開到有人理為止"},{"pid":"ef3e006c771b26b2d12d7e373caae1e3841e6b15","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40fbacab4e3da357b935e4d29885fbfb67f0ca5f","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:29:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae89af0f80f305c2dab9e7b4d4d142be88d1ec0f","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:30:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"233c0fe5ea004f51a095f08537fe48854ea0b026","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:30:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e764d5427893bccf546c63a09e073870be10871d","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"fb ig WeChat 微博 全撚部都要見到"},{"pid":"2404cf353d7ff7b6c6b870b614e4735549246acd","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c0a0cb4ab0a3465dbab65ff5b834e5d9edb917b","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:31:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96671e730f932d98ab98f7139b3b0729abcf49a4","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2bb933b00646e1ccb9a2bf227dcad1495f8e218c","tid":1474580,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:32:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b264952a0561c5312ec2c458066a765eb7c315e","tid":1474580,"uid":106093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:32:25.000Z","msg":"816晚啊"},{"pid":"a98dcdf7f8b34eac6be65a35588c